data.title: Nadezhda Sergejevna “Nadya” Alliluyeva Stalina ...
data.meta_description: Soviet Russian Figure. She was the second wife of Josef Vissarionovich Stalin. Stalin  married Allilujeva in 1918, and she was young enough to be his daugter. Allilujewa never fit in the political environment of her husband, she became outsider and she was very unhappy. She was found dead in her sleeping room with one...
